  * kvm_gpc_gpa - retrieve the guest physical address of a cached mapping
  *
  * @gpc:	   struct gfn_to_pfn_cache object.
+ *
+ * @return:	   If the cache was activated with a fixed HVA then INVALID_GPA
+ *		   will be returned.
